<p begin='00:00:05.873' end='00:00:07.074' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]<br/>&gt;&gt; Jon: WELCOME BACK.</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:07.107' end='00:00:10.611' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>MY GUEST TONIGHT, HE IS THE HOST<br/>OF CNN&apos;S &quot;FAREED ZAKARIA GPS.&quot;</span></p>
