<p begin='00:00:32.032' end='00:00:37.371' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]<br/>CAN I TELL YOU SOMETHING?</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:37.404' end='00:00:41.975' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>OUR FAKE KICK STARTER TO BUY CNN<br/>IS UP TO $150 BILLION NOW.</span></p>
