<p begin='00:03:21.802' end='00:03:22.936' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; WELL, AS YOU KNOW, HE USED TO<br/>BE... THERE WAS A TIME WHEN</span></p>
