<p begin='00:03:56.203' end='00:03:56.904' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; SO IT&apos;S ALMOST LIKE THE<br/>DEMOCRATIZATION OF VIOLENCE,</span></p>
